transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks Yvonne Viagra, Quinn speaking. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, my husband and I are trying to get his subscription cancelled and we sent an email but they said that we had to call and speak to an agent on the phone.

Speaker 1: Okay, what is the phone number that you have on file with us?

Speaker 2: 210-708-8369.

Speaker 1: One moment.

Speaker 2: And what is your zip code?

Speaker 1: 78108.

Speaker 2: And what was the first and last name?

Speaker 1: First name is Ty, T-Y. Last name Burnham, B-U-R-N-A-M.

Speaker 2: Alrighty, and is your husband available to give you the okay to cancel it?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I can try to add him onto the call. He was on hold earlier but couldn't wait any longer.

Speaker 2: Give me one second.

Speaker 1: If that doesn't work, I can just give you my extension and he can call back in when he can and it would go directly to my number.

Speaker 2: Okay, let me see if he'll answer real fast.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Okay, you should both be there.

Speaker 1: Hello?

Speaker 2: Hello?

Speaker 1: Sir?

Speaker 2: Yes, sir, I just wanted to get confirmation you wanted to cancel your account here.

Speaker 1: Yes, this is Ty Burnham.

Speaker 2: Okay, and you guys definitely didn't want to order as needed or anything like that?

Speaker 1: Was it that it was coming too fast for you?

Speaker 2: I just don't need it.

Speaker 1: Okay, just asking.

Speaker 2: Alright, we'll go ahead and cancel it out for you.

Speaker 1: Alright, thank you very much.

Speaker 2: You're welcome.

Speaker 1: Have a good day.

Speaker 2: Thank you.
